Path Recruitment Message 2

Date: 02/03/2023

Day 2 of our recruitment drive is here and we would like to extend a warm invitation to join us on The Path. We are a team of evolved mutants dedicated to creating a better future for all of our kind. And we need your help!

As a scientist, you bring a unique set of skills and knowledge to the table that can make a real difference in the fight against Doc Gibbons and his Mega Mutant friends. Your contributions will not only benefit The Path but also help advance the cause of mutantkind as a whole.

So why wait? Join us on The Path today and help shape a better tomorrow for mutants everywhere.

Together, we are unstoppable.

Join us and be a part of The Path. 
